 michael kors building at the nonprofit’s new soho headquarters in honor of kors’ ongoing support  selected for the time  the magazines annual list of the  most influential people in the world he also made the new york observers list of the  most influential new yorkers under the fashion category and was named to out magazine’s  power  list  honored with the  couture council award for artistry of fashion by the couture council of the museum at the fashion institute of technology  kors presented hillary rodham clinton with the firstever michael kors award for outstanding community service  honored with the golden heart lifetime achievement award by gods love we deliver a nonprofit organization that distributes fresh meals to people living with hivaids and other diagnoses which he has been involved with for over  years  received the oliver r grace award for distinguished service in advancing cancer research an annual honor bestowed by the cancer research institute a us nonprofit organization dedicated to advancing immune systembased treatments for cancer  kors was the youngest recipient ever of the geoffrey beene lifetime achievement award from the council of fashion designers of america cfda and received the fragrance foundation’s fifi award for lifetime achievement legal issuesedit in january  the estate of the artistdesigner tony duquette sued kors for trademark infringement after kors allegedly used duquettes name and images in promoting kors  resortwear collection in july  he became the second luxury brand after tiffany  co to sue costco for falsely claiming in advertisements that they sold his product in popular cultureedit kors was referenced in the film the devil wears prada by meryl streeps character miranda priestly in the scene priestly sweeps into her office and gives a list of instructions to her personal assistant emily blunt priestly says rsvp yes to michael kors party and i want the driver to drop me off at  and pick me up at  sharp kors is also mentioned in big seans song dance by nicki minaj drake also mentions michael kors in his song from time and rapper pusha t in his song numbers on the boards additionally kors guest starred as himself in a fashion week themed episode of the hit teen show gossip girl the same show that repeatedly showcases several pieces from his collections referencesedit  solomon brian  february  michael kors is fashions newest billionaire forbes retrieved  april    a b lee joyce august   designer michael kors marries longtime partner cbs news retrieved october     kors show a knockout opulence glitz dominate wardrobes daily news new york february   archived from the original on november     the michael kors story stylsh   a b hw wilson company  current biography h w wilson co p    harpers bazaar michael kors american idol by elisa lipskykarasz june     archived may   at the wayback machine  a b people magazine with his hot new line michael kors grabs the fashion ladders top rung by elizabeth sporkin april    rappaport jill november  mazel tov celebrities bar and bat mitzvah memories simon  schuster isbn    andreoli richard  working the runway out designer michael kors tells it like it is to wouldbe fashionistas on bravos project runway the advocate archived from the original on  retrieved    michael kors interview magazine   rathe adam august   michael kors marries longtime boyfriend lance lepere in barefoot southampton beach ceremony new york daily news retrieved april     a b michael kors vogue archived from the original on december     lafaille rena  june  seven surprising facts about michael kors abc news retrieved  october    kilcooleyohalloran scarlett january   michael kors vogue retrieved april     infomat michael kors biography infomatcom september    michael kors retails next billiondollar man cnncom   the michael kors story december    wilson eric february   mrs obama in kors the new york times retrieved march     pezik anna august   gwyneth paltrow possession cnncom archive r