rrivals categories for her for him gift services gift cards shops the monogram shop custom kors fragrance wearable technology our best gifts categories view all sale handbags wallets watches clothing shoes jewelry  accessories michael kors collection men trends new to sale michael kors  reality television star fashion designer model  biographycomsubscribe to newsletteraboutmichael kors biographycomreality television star fashion designer model–sharesquick factsnamemichael korsoccupationreality television star fashion designer modelbirth dateaugust   age educationfashion institute of technologyplace of birthlong island new yorkoriginallykarl anderson jrakakarl andersonmichael korsfull namemichael david korszodiac signleocite this pagemichael kors is an american fashion designer best known for serving as a judge on the popular television show project runway hes also known for designing michelle obamas dress for her first official portraitin these groupsfamous people born on august reality tv starsfamous fashion designersfamous people born in long islandshow all groupsfamous people born in united statesfamous fashion institute of technology alumnifamous leosname changersfamous people born in fashion front rowfamous modelsfamous people who launched clothing and jewelry linesfamous people named michaelfamous people born in new yorkfamous people named korsquotes“now that valentino has retired i believe someone must wave the tootanned flag”michael korssynopsismichael kors was born on august   on long island new york he moved to new york city to attend the fashion institute of technology but dropped out after two semesters kors launched his womens collection in  and became a judge on project runway in  first lady michelle obama posed in a michael kors dress for her first official portrait kors lives in new york cityearly lifeborn karl anderson jr on long island new york on august   famed fashion designer michael david kors was raised on new yorks long island as a toddler kors worked as a model appearing in national campaigns for products such as toilet paper and lucky charms cereal korss biological parents split when he was quite young and he got his new name at the age of  when his mother married businessman bill kors my mother said youre getting a new last name so why dont you pick a new first name kors recalled he chose michael as his first name and his secondfavorite david as his middle name his mother also allowed him to design her wedding dress kors already a fashion addict was thrilled with the prospect the marriage didnt last but the pictures are timeless kors quipped laterfrom their suburban home in merrick new york kors scavenged every bit of fashion intelligence he could gather i practically hyperventilated every month when vogue arrived and i loved shopping he said kors moved to new york city in the s to attend the fashion institute of technology he loved the city more than the school however and dropped out after two semesters in  kors went to work at the french boutique lothars which allowed him to design and merchandise his first fashion collection the wellreceived collection generated enough interest that kors was able to start his own fashion line michael kors womens collection launched in may  and was sold in the highend department stores bergdorf goodman and saks fifth avenuefashion design successkorss simple elegantly tailored clothing and his charmingly persuasive sales techniques proved to be a winning combination kors traveled across the united states for small fashion shows at private homes known as trunk shows when he was  he convinced the formidable fashion editor anna wintour—then of new york magazine now the editor of vogue—to view his collection the glitzy madison avenue showrooms hed later have were still a long way off kors displayed the collection laid out on his bed in his apartment from these humble beginnings he soon picked up celebrity fans like barbara walters and earned awards for his designsin  however kors company was forced to reorganize under chapter  bankruptcy after getting back on his feet kors launched kors michael kors a lowerpriced line he also became the creative director of celine a french fashion house in  in the six years he held that position he continued to expand his own brand launching menswear accessory and perfume lines in  he won the coveted menswear designer of the year award from the council of fashion designers of america the most prestigious prize in american fashionproject runwayin  kors was asked to be a judge on a new reality television show called project runway he almost turned it down reality show fashion on television kors recalled thinking i thought that only fashionista freaks gays and men wanting to see heidi klum in a short dress would watch it he was wrong the show premiered on december   and became an immediate hit with fans and critics korss quips and blunt criticisms were fan favorites and he continued as a judge in subsequent seasons viewers of project runway often commented on his perennial tan a source of pride for the beachloving kors now that valentino has retired i believe someone must wave the tootanned flag the designer joked in  kors announced that he would be retiring from project runway by that time the series had garnered several emmy award nominations among other honorspersonal lifejust a few weeks after gay marriage became legal in new york kors married his longtime partner lance la pere vice president of michael kors womens design in august  the pair had first met in  when la pere was an intern at the companycountless celebrities wear his garments and us first lady michelle obama posed in a michael kors dress for her first official portrait with new lines constantly in production and more customers drawn in by his project runway appearances korss fashion empire continues to growfact checkwe strive for accuracy and fairness if you see something that doesnt look right contact uscitation informationarticle