could i wear this could i wear it to work to dinner or drinks will it span the seasons if you have to think too hard about those questions then skip it michael kors work yourself dinner my legacy would be that you dont have to give up anything you can be chic but have a sense of humor you can be sexy but comfortable you can be timeless but fresh michael kors humor sexy legacy for me true luxury can be caviar or a day with no meetings no appointments and no schedule michael kors day meetings me i grew up surrounded by these tough ballsy strong women they were also adoring women but they were the kind of women who would argue over what kind of pants you were wearing or the color of your nail polish michael kors women strong color when i was a kid i was trendier id wear anything i was in love beads and platforms michael kors love kid platforms i think the older i get the more i realize that the ultimate luxury is time michael kors time realize think learn to invest in the best quality you can afford and wear pieces in different ways michael kors best quality learn the biggest lesson that ive learned is that fashion is this tightrope where you have to be consistent but inconsistent you need the connective thread but at the same time you need a sense of surprise michael kors time fashion surprise i know what women look good in i dont think the rules ever change michael kors change women good people want to look taller and thinner no one says ooh let me buy that dress because it makes me feel matronly michael kors dress look people americans are always a little bit insecure michael kors little always little bit clothes are like a good meal a good movie great pieces of music michael kors music good great i am the oldest young designer in new york city michael kors i am city young give me caviar kaspia and give me a hamburger i love the two extremes michael kors love me two i wasnt barbieobsessed i think my mother might have been my barbie michael kors mother think been i wear the same thing every day i always pack two black jackets loads of black tshirts loads of white jeans i feel a little fresh and glamorous and graphic michael kors day black white i grew up in a family of people who were obsessed with fashion michael kors family fashion people my apartment looks like no one lives in it michael kors looks apartment like my mom was a model she had me at  so she was a young mother michael kors mother mom me i think a lot of women have too many mini skirts in their closets michael kors women think skirts north americans as a whole need to embrace having clothes altered to their body i hear it all the time why do the europeans always look so good they have a relationship with their tailor and spend the time and money to make their clothes look their best michael kors time relationship money i cant dance and i cant sing too well michael kors dance sing well theres a whole generation of women who never really heard the word investment before when it came to fashion theyve been buying things because they were cheap michael kors women fashion generation share this page cite this page citation find on amazon michael kors related authors vera wang calvin klein tom ford marc jacobs ralph lauren charles eames donna karan paul rand brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site home authors topics quote of the day pictures top  quotes professions birthdays social bq on facebook bq on twitter bq on pinterest bq on google bq on instagram shop brainyquote store apps iphoneipad app quote of the day feeds javascript and rss feeds wordpress plugin quote of the day email about about us contact us submit privacy terms copyright     brainyquote   loading load more quotes microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring you